            "label": "Controls and Monitoring section of this guide",
            "data_guide_link": "system:controls"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "S7",
        "sentence": "The ACR Manual Control Override Knob takes manual control of bank combine and isolate. Use it when:\n\n- you need to combine battery banks manually\n- remote operation must be blocked\n- the ACR must be secured for servicing",
        "sources": [
          "graph.device:blue_sea_acr",
          "profile.blue_sea_acr.operator_actions",
          "profile.blue_sea_acr.control_surfaces"
        ],
        "kind": "sourced",
        "block": "adjusting"
      },
      {
        "id": "S8",
        "sentence": "Use the local rotary isolation switch when that battery connection must be disconnected at the switch.",
        "sources": [
          "graph.device:plain_battery_switch",
          "profile.plain_battery_switch.operator_actions"
        ],
        "kind": "sourced",
        "block": "adjusting"
      },
      {
        "id": "S9",
        "sentence": "If a bank connection drops unexpectedly, confirm ACR combine/isolate state and Class-T fuse integrity before restoring loads. BMS reset steps can be found in the Batteries & Energy section of this guide.",
        "sources": [
          "graph.device:blue_sea_acr",
          "graph.device:class_t_1",
          "graph.device:class_t_2",
          "graph.device:class_t_3",
          "profile.class_t.safety_role.is_protective_device",
          "xref.batteries"
        ],
        "kind": "sourced",
        "block": "troubleshooting",
        "links": [
          {
            "target_kind": "system",
            "target_id": "batteries",
            "label": "Batteries & Energy section of this guide",
            "data_guide_link": "system:batteries"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "S10",
        "sentence": "The DC distribution busbar (ProInstaller) in the Engine / Machinery Space – Engine Bay — a heavy-duty conductor that distributes power — is the main power distribution point behind those protected connections.",
        "sources": [
          "graph.device:busbar",
          "equipment.busbar",
          "equipment.busbar.places"
        ],
        "kind": "sourced",
        "block": "reference"
      },
      {
        "id": "S11",
        "sentence": "The MasterBus–CZone bridge (Mastervolt MasterBus Bridge Interface) allows MasterBus equipment and the CZone network to exchange status and control across that boundary.",
        "sources": [
          "graph.device:masterbus_bridge_interface",
          "equipment.masterbus_bridge_interface.description"
        ],
        "kind": "sourced",
        "block": "reference"
      },
      {
